#
1 show processlist to dispay all active process, you can also use the kill command
2 joins, unions, subqueries
3 explain
4 stored procedure execute quicker than individual statements.
5 use the right data types
6 never retrieve more data than you need.
7 when importing data, turn off autocommit, drop indexes and the recreate
them after completed.
8 have a series of complex or conditions in your select? improve by union.
9 indexes improve the performance of data retrieval but hurt the performance 
of data insertion, deletion, and updating.
10 like is slow. use fulltext over like.
